data.description: It's time to take a drive over to Park Lane South and stop into your new apartment! Stately and timeless Park Lane South Condominium was once home to the William Demuth Pipe Factory and can now be yours. Beautiful building has since been converted into lovely loft-style units complete with high ceilings and huge light-filled windows. Through the front door you are greeted by an outstanding and desirable open floorplan that offers an oversized open kitchen with breakfast bar, cozy dining area, and huge living room. Down the hall are two equally sized and spacious bedrooms with excellent closet space. In the hall there is a half bath that contains the laundry as well as the full main bathroom. Exceptional opportunity in a great neighborhood that just needs your ideas, visions, plans, and personal touches to make it absolutely perfect and pleasant. Start building equity today and schedule your showing!
